<p>Thanks AJWW for his frank and generous criticism. [See <hi rend="doubleUnderline">9352</hi>.] Having viewed all natural objects under the light of natural selection for more than thirty years, CD thinks it unlikely that any arguments short of demonstration can convince him of error.</p> 
